Introduction

Rocking doll (Korean: 록킹돌) is a four-member girl group under SRP Entertainment. They debuted on December 19, 2021 with the self-titled digital single "Rocking Doll".

On April 1, 2022, SRP announced that Rena would be going on a hiatus due to health reasons and that the group would then continue as a three-member group until Rena's return. On February 24, 2023, SRP announced that Juri will also be going on a hiatus due to health reasons. On June 20, 2023 SRP announced that Ahri will be going on a hiatus in order to focus on her studies for the qualification exam in August.
